    <S id="S_1">
        <FORM>ru taqru' i kumayi' su quriyux ga baqun su musa' tana' i pamuwaun la ga ga hawbingun la.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 生薑挖完，知道到達夠種的數量後，就把他們切塊。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> (We) finish digging out the ginger, and when the amount is known to be enough for planting, we have them cut.</TRANSL>
