    <S id="S_5">
        <FORM>ru i taqaru' i taqarun niyam ku waw niyam la ga talan ru ki'man ku quriyux niyam la ga musa' sami i halan niyam tumuba' ru su skuan su xiliyu'.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 而且，我們完成我們的工作之後，看到我們的生薑長草，我們會去噴藥(除草劑)，並且施肥。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> And, after we finish our work, when seeing grass growing around our ginger, we'll go to spray insecticide and add fertilizer.</TRANSL>
