    <S id="S_7">
        <FORM>tiku asi syue syue hani la ga sipayat cu buwating hani la ga usu i i ta'ali' la ru musa' sumliyat ru taqaruun sumlyat la ga luma talan ru kiya ku ali' la ga mana'aring i tabalku' la.</FORM>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="zh"> 就像這個四月，我們會去採竹筍，而且會去砍草。然後砍完草之後，(如果)看到有竹筍，就開始採竹筍。</TRANSL>
        <TRANSL xml:lang="en"> Just like this April, (we) would gather bamboo shoots, and go to cut grass. And after cutting the grass, (if we) see there are bamboo shoots, we'll start to gather them.</TRANSL>
